      "date": "2018-03-16 13:40:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nSorry I was away on a business trip. I see what happened. Originally the stats code was moved to debugfs but this prevented non-root users from using stats. So I removed that change from the LU-8066 patch. I missed that echo server code uses stats so yes we need to restore /proc for now for this driver.",
